- Lucide React (ISC License) - https://lucide.dev/

### Backend Dependencies
- FastAPI (MIT License) - https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/
- Python (PSF License) - https://www.python.org/
- NumPy (BSD License) - https://numpy.org/
- Pillow (HPND License) - https://python-pillow.org/
- OpenCV (Apache 2.0) - https://opencv.org/
- GDAL (MIT/X License) - https://gdal.org/
- Rasterio (BSD License) - https://rasterio.readthedocs.io/

### AI & Services
- Google Earth Engine (proprietary, requires license)
- Ollama (MIT License) - https://ollama.ai/

### Data Sources
- Sentinel-2 satellite imagery (ESA, free and open)
- SRTM elevation data (NASA/USGS, public domain)

